=\"bd\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><span class=\"ba\">abrdn plc </span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold\"><span class=\"ay\">(\"the Company\")</span></span></p>\n<p class=\"be\"><span class=\"ay\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p class=\"be\"><span class=\"ay\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p class=\"bf\"><span class=\"av\">Statement regarding potential acquisition</span></p>\n<p class=\"bg\"><span class=\"at\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p class=\"bh\"><span class=\"ay\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p class=\"bh\"><span class=\"ay\">The Company notes recent media speculation and confirms that it is currently in discussions with J.C. Flowers &amp; Co regarding a potential acquisition of Interactive Investor.\u00a0 </span></p>\n<p class=\"bh\"><span class=\"ay\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p class=\"bh\"><span class=\"ay\">There can be no certainty that these discussions will result in a transaction and a further announcement by the Company will be made as and when appropriate.</span></p>\n<p class=\"bh\"><span class=\"ay\">\u00a0</span></p>\n<p class=\"bh\"><span class=\"bi\">8 November 2021</span></p>\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n<p class=\"be\">Enquiries:</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n<div class=\"story-table-container\"><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"bj\" style=\"width:602\">\n<tr>\n<td class=\"aq\" style=\"width:55%\">\n<p class=\"be\">Analysts/Institutional Investors</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">Catherine Nash</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"ap\" style=\"width:44%\">\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">+44 (0) 7798 518 657</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"aq\" style=\"width:55%\">\n<p class=\"be\">Media</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">Stephen Whitehead\u00a0</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"ap\" style=\"width:44%\">\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">+44 (0) 7920 369 595</p>\n<p class=\"bh\">\u00a0</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td class=\"aq\" style=\"width:55%\">\n<p class=\"be\